OPTIMAL_MERGE_PATTERNS(n, arr)
1. Sort the array arr in non-decreasing order.
2. Initialize a variable total_cost to 0.
3. While the length of arr is greater than 1:
     a. Take the first two elements of arr and add them together. This represents the cost of merging two files.
     b. Add the cost to total_cost.
     c. Append the sum to arr.
     d. Remove the first two elements of arr.
4. Return total_cost.
